lakshyam ( english : target ) is a 2007 telugu film produced by nallamalupu srinivas ( bujji ) on sri lakshmi narasimha productions banner and directed by srivass .   starring gopichand , jagapati babu , anushka in lead roles and music composed by mani sharma .   the film recorded as super hit at box office .   it was later remade in tamil as maanja velu , in bengali as fighter and in kannada as varadhanayaka .   the movie was dubbed in hindi as bhai - the lion and in malayalam as chandu - the hot her .